 <fr:p>By <fr:link
href="jms-00IM.xml"
title="Relational extensionality"
addr="jms-00IM"
type="local">relational extensionality</fr:link>, it suffices to check that for any <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x\in  \mathbb {R}_{\geq  0}]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[y\in  \mathbb {R}]]></fr:tex>, we have <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x\mathrel {{\mathopen {}\left (\mathsf {neg}\circ \mathsf {sq}\right )\mathclose {}}} y]]></fr:tex> if and only if <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x\mathrel {\mathsf {sq}}y]]></fr:tex>. We compute:</fr:p>

 <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[
  \begin {aligned}
   x\mathrel {{\mathopen {}\left (\mathsf {neg}\circ \mathsf {sq}\right )\mathclose {}}} y
   &\Longleftrightarrow 
   \exists  z\in \mathbb {R}\mathpunct {.}
   x\mathrel {\mathsf {sq}}z \land  z \mathrel {\mathsf {neg}}y
   \\
   &\Longleftrightarrow 
   \exists  z\in \mathbb {R}\mathpunct {.}
   x=z^2 \land  z =-y
   \\
   &\Longleftrightarrow 
   x={\mathopen {}\left (-y\right )\mathclose {}}^2
   \\
   &\Longleftrightarrow 
   x = y^2
   \\
   &\Longleftrightarrow 
   x\mathrel {\mathsf {sq}}y
  \end {aligned}
 ]]></fr:tex>
</fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter><fr:tree
